## Notes
- URL: https://github.com/Augani/openreel-video
- Core Features:
    - Multi-track timeline, multi-layer assets (video, audio, image, text).
    - WebGPU rendering, AI upscaling.
    - Professional tools: Undo/Redo (Action system), keyframes, audio mixing, beat detection.
    - Export: MP4, WebM, ProRes (ffmpeg.wasm + WebCodecs).
- Why CapCut alternative:
    - 100% browser-based, no installation, professional tools, no watermarks.
- Programmatic Control:
    - Uses a `Zustand` store and an "Action Dispatch" system. Agents can programmatically trigger actions (AddClip, MoveClip, etc.) to edit videos.
    - Clear architecture (Video, Audio, Graphics, Text, Timeline, Export modules).
- AI Features:
    - AI Upscaling (Completed).
    - Auto-captions/Text-to-Video: Not explicitly in the current roadmap, but extensible via its plugin/action system.
